### Health Check
GET http://localhost:3000/health

### Get Rankings (Public)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/ranking

### Get Player Profile (Replace 'test_user' with an actual username in Supabase)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/players/test_user

### Get Player Match History (Replace 'test_user' with an actual username)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/players/test_user/history?page=1&limit=10

### Login Admin to get Token
# @name login
POST http://localhost:3000/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "admin",
  "password": "admin12345"
}

### Retrieve Token from Response
@authToken = {{login.response.body.token}}

### Trigger Refresh Ranking (Protected - requires Login first)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/admin/cron/refresh-ranking
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### Toggle Player Status to Banned (Protected - replace ':id' with actual profile ID)
PUT http://localhost:3000/api/admin/players/1/status
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "banned"
}
